{"tid":707833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普反擊 或對中國貨品追加1.56萬億新關稅","createTime":"2018-06-19T02:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T02:20:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b852ff9121e7b5f10f404aaf1fea494572339a8","tid":707833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】美國特朗普於周一指示美國貿易代表，準備對中國進口貨品的2000億美元（1.56萬億港元）新關稅，進行反擊，令中美兩國貿易戰再度升級。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普打算以「10％稅率」制定新關稅，以回應他所指的兩國巨大貿易不平衡的懲罰措施。特朗普於聲明中表示，「中國顯然無意改變與收購美國知識產權和技術有關的不公平做法」，又批評中國正威脅美國公司、工人和農民。<br />\n<br />\n他又再指出，「如果中國拒絕改變其做法，又堅持推行最近公佈的新關稅，這些關稅將生效。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A-%E6%88%96%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%81%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A01-56%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-003900636.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E5%258A%25A01-56%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585-003900636.html&d=R0oyRw0%2F7CAxgVAVebxmzAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6b5bb81b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A-%E6%88%96%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%81%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A01-56%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-003900636.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a148e7e3d32280347ebd189acdf52d644ddc78","tid":707833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"1.56萬億<br />\n<br />\n唔慣睇天文數字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}